00:32:06.000 --> 00:32:08.000
and have that component react to all the

00:32:08.000 --> 00:32:10.000
other components as well.

00:32:10.000 --> 00:32:12.000
So that's possible today,

00:32:12.000 --> 00:32:14.000
we have written it down, we're in today

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:16.000
writing it down, and so that's

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:18.000
another thing that, and that's

00:32:18.000 --> 00:32:20.000
again, the history

00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:22.000
of shiny is from

00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:24.000
people who did web development, JavaScript web development,

00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:26.000
so that's kind of like

